snippet.title: Meghan FACE LIKE THUNDER After 'CONTROL FREAK' Accurse SURFACED, Claim Harry Spending MONITORED
snippet.description:
Meghan FACE LIKE THUNDER After 'CONTROL FREAK' Accurse SURFACED, Claim Harry Spending MONITORED
👉👉 Join Us In Telegram - UK Royal News : https://t.me/ukroyalnews
👉👉Watch the latest video at: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLOmZC3x6H9EbCfXxP8k88csus6Z5JUpGD

Prince Harry and Meghan Markle are once again embroiled in a major controversy in relation to Omid Scobie and Carolyn Durand’s book, Finding Freedom. The couple is being accused of lying, and their credibility is also being questioned by royal experts and critics.
Amid the ongoing talks regarding Prince Harry and Meghan Markle’s involvement in the book, a new allegation surfaced regarding the couple.

Life & Style, in its Nov. 29 issue, claimed that the Duke and Duchess of Sussex are dealing with spending issues behind closed doors.
A source claimed that Markle always wants to be in control to the point that she monitors Prince Harry’s credit card spending.
“Meghan says she’s just being mindful of their finances since she grew up on a budget, but checking Harry’s credit card statement definitely crosses the henpecked line. He’s a grown man who can check his own statements. Meghan clearly likes being in control, though. She doesn’t like surprises,” the unnamed source said.
The allegations surfaced shortly after Markle sat down for an interview at the New York Times Deal Book Online Summit earlier this month. At the time, the Suits alum said that she doesn’t buy anything online without first looking for promo codes first.
Markle didn’t mention Prince Harry’s spending during her interview, but the unnamed source claimed that the rule of using promo codes also applies to her husband.
Since they stepped down from the firm in March, 2020. It is belied that Meghan Has taken totally control over prince harry
Those close to the Royal Family say they believe the Duchess is the driving force behind the Sussexes move to quit the royal family. As the PRINCE has “completely changed” since meeting Meghan Markle.
